A) Introduction

Transform your insurance agency's online presence with the Insurerity HTML template, meticulously crafted to redefine digital engagement and enhance your firm's credibility. Designed with a sleek and professional aesthetic, Insurerity seamlessly combines elegance with functionality, offering a robust platform to showcase your insurance solutions, attract clients, and fortify your brand identity.

Immerse your visitors in a visually captivating journey while communicating your agency's expertise with clarity and authority. Navigate through Insurerity's versatile features, empowering you to effortlessly customize and personalize your website. From highlighting insurance products and services to featuring client success stories and agent profiles, Insurerity provides a comprehensive toolkit for crafting a compelling digital strategy aligned with your agency's objectives.

Establish trust and credibility with Insurerity's responsive design, ensuring a seamless user experience across desktops, tablets, and smartphones. Compatible with all modern browsers and optimized for search engines, Insurerity enables you to effectively reach and engage a wider audience.

Unlock the potential of your insurance agency and embark on a journey of digital excellence with Insurerity. Whether you're a local agency or a national provider, Insurerity is tailored to meet your unique needs and empower you to thrive in today's competitive insurance marketplace.

Featuring 3 distinct Home Page layouts, an About Page template, and 19 meticulously designed HTML5 page templates, Insurerity offers versatility and style. Built with Bootstrap v4.6.2, HTML5, and CSS3, and offering unlimited color schemes, Insurerity ensures your website not only looks stunning but performs flawlessly across all devices. Elevate your agency's online presence with Insurerity and showcase your services with confidence.

It also contains different Blog page style and unlimited color schemes. It’s compatible with all modern browsers and search engine friendly. So showcase your artworks and services with this awesome template!

B) How to Edit HTML Files?

We have included 23 custom HTML templates like Home Page, About, Services, Portfolio and Contact etc. Please open any HTML files with a text editor like Dreamweaver, Notepad or Notepad++ and edit any lines what you want.

C) How to Edit CSS Files?

We have included some custom CSS styles like style.css (default). Please open any CSS files with a text editor like Dreamweaver, Notepad or Notepad++ and edit any lines what you want. For example if you want to edit your banner color open style.css and look at ".banner-con" for banner image and change your image.

 

D) How to use Color Schemes?

Please open style.css file from Insurerity/assets/css folder with a text editor and build your own colors. #141430 this is our primary color, you can search and replace all to your new color code.

 

E) How to use On Load Animation?

We are AJVhOs3EUusBmbyJu6FUMdqU.js on load animation for our website. you can edit them by simply adding or changeing the predefined classes name.
